  "page": 162,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0002",
      "text": " 143",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0003",
      "text": "unpredictable.  If an Nx_Port receives a Logout request while another Sequence is open that was ini-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.99,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0004",
      "text": "tiated from the requesting Nx_Port, it may reject the Logout request using an LS_RJT (Link Service",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        539.92,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0005",
      "text": "Reject).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        130.36,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0006",
      "text": "After an explicit Logout is performed with an Nx_Port, the default Login Service Parameters specified",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.98,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0007",
      "text": "in table 150 and table 155 shall be functional if Login was explicit.  After an explicit Logout is per-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        539.5,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0008",
      "text": "formed with an Nx_Port, the implicit Login Service Parameters shall be functional if Login was implic-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        539.97,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0009",
      "text": "it.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        103.75,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0010",
      "text": "6.4.3",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        118.22,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0011",
      "text": "Explicit Fabric Logout",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        166.96,
        233.18,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0012",
      "text": "Explicit Fabric Logout of an N_Port_ID shall be accomplished by transmitting a Logout (LOGO) Link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        539.98,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0013",
      "text": "Service request Sequence (see 4.2.8) from an Nx_Port to an Fx_Port (i.e., Well-known address",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.57,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0014",
      "text": "FFFFFEh) or from an Fx_Port to an Nx_Port. The explicit Fabric Logout procedure shall be complete",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.76,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0015",
      "text": "for the responding FC_Port when it transmits a LS_ACC Link Service reply Sequence. The explicit",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        540.0,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0016",
      "text": "Fabric Logout procedure shall be complete for the requesting FC_Port when it receives a LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.05,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0017",
      "text": "Link Service reply Sequence.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        225.46,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0018",
      "text": "If an FC_Port that does not support explicit Fabric Logout receives a LOGO that requests explicit",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        539.97,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0019",
      "text": "Fabric Logout, it shall reject the explicit Fabric Logout request using an LS_RJT with reason code",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        539.83,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0020",
      "text": "\"Command not supported\" and reason code explanation \"No additional explanation\". If an FC_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        540.08,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0021",
      "text": "that sends a LOGO that requests explicit Fabric Logout receives in reply an LS_RJT with reason",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        539.95,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0022",
      "text": "code \"Command not supported\" and reason code explanation \"No additional explanation\" the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        539.92,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0023",
      "text": "FC_Port that sent the LOGO shall implicitly log out the other FC_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        404.27,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0024",
      "text": "An Fx_Port that supports N_Port_ID virtualization shall support explicit Fabric Logout originated by",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        539.99,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0025",
      "text": "an Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        148.75,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0026",
      "text": "An Nx_Port that has requested or accepted explicit Fabric Logout of an N_Port_ID shall implicitly log",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        540.01,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0027",
      "text": "out the N_Port_ID with all other N_Port_IDs with which the N_Port_ID was logged in, and shall not",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.93,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0028",
      "text": "originate frames from the N_Port_ID until after it has subsequently been reassigned the N_Port_ID",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.92,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0029",
      "text": "by the Fabric. An Fx_Port that has explicitly logged out an N_Port_ID shall neither originate nor route",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        539.97,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0030",
      "text": "frames to the N_Port_ID until after it has completed a subsequent reassignment of the N_Port_ID.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        528.76,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0031",
      "text": "6.4.4",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        118.22,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0032",
      "text": "Implicit Logout",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        466.96,
        199.84,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0033",
      "text": "If an Nx_Port receives or transmits an NOS or OLS, it shall be implicitly logged out from the Fabric, if",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        539.96,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0034",
      "text": "present, or attached Nx_Port in a point-to-point topology. Communication with other Nx_Ports shall",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        539.84,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0035",
      "text": "not be accepted until the Fabric Login procedure is complete (implicit or explicit).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        451.51,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0036",
      "text": "During Login with the Fabric, if the Nx_Port detects that the N_Port_ID, F_Port_Name and/or the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        539.93,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0037",
      "text": "Fabric_Name has changed since the last Fabric Login, and the Clean Address bit is zero, the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        539.97,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0038",
      "text": "Nx_Port shall implicitly logout with all Nx_Ports and wait an R_A_TOV timeout period before initiating",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        539.92,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0039",
      "text": "or accepting communication with other Nx_Ports.  The timeout period shall start when the Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        540.01,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0040",
      "text": "detects the change.  After waiting the timeout period, new N_Port Logins are required before the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        539.78,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0041",
      "text": "Nx_Port may communicate with other Nx_Ports.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        308.77,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0042",
      "text": "During Login with the Fabric, if the Nx_Port detects that the N_Port_ID, F_Port_Name and/or the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.94,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p162_s0043",
      "text": "Fabric_Name has changed since the last Fabric Login, and the Clean Address bit is set to one, the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.02,
        539.81,
        646.13
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}